<h1>Privacy Policy for KITAPHANA</h1>
<p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> 18.04.2025</p>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
<p>We may collect the following types of data:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> such as name, email address (only if provided voluntarily, e.g., for account creation).</li>
    <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> including device type, OS version, and app usage statistics.</li>
    <li><strong>Book Data:</strong> such as saved books, reading status (e.g., “Reading”, “Finished”), and preferences.</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>We use the data to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Provide and improve app functionality.</li>
    <li>Save and sync your reading preferences.</li>
    <li>Offer personalized book recommendations (if available).</li>
    <li>Respond to support queries.</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Data Sharing and Third Parties</h2>
<p>We do <strong>not sell</strong> or share your personal data with third parties, except:</p>
<ul>
    <li>When required by law or government authorities.</li>
    <li>With trusted services for analytics etc..</li>
</ul>

<h2>4. Children’s Privacy</h2>
<p>Our app is <strong>not directed to children under 13</strong>. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children. If you believe we have collected such data, please contact us immediately at <strong>archsoft.bil@gmail.com</strong>.</p>

<h2>5. Data Security</h2>
<p>We take reasonable steps to protect your data using encryption and secure services. However, no system is 100% secure.</p>

<h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
<p>You may request to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>View or delete your personal data.</li>
    <li>Withdraw your consent to data collection.</li>
</ul>
<p>Contact us at <strong>archsoft.bil@gmail.com</strong> for such requests.</p>

<h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted in-app and/or on our store listing.</p>

<h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
<p>If you have any questions or concerns about this policy, reach out at:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Email:</strong> archsoft.bil@gmail.com</li>
    <li><strong>Developer Name:</strong> ArchSoft</li>
</ul>
